sources.title: Asteroid-a-Geddon | Full Movie | Action Sci-Fi Disaster | Eric Roberts
sources.description:
Asteroid-a-Geddon - A global summit fails repeatedly to stop a massive asteroid headed straight for Earth. With the outlook now bleak, a young tech genius assembles her own team of specialists, using cutting edge aeronautics, in a last ditch effort to stop the asteroid before it’s too late.
2020.  Stars: Eric Roberts, Veronika Issa, Jennifer Lee Wiggins

metadata.Plot: A global scientific summit debates and fails on a plan to stop a massive asteroid heading straight for Earth, with all countries blaming each other for the impeding disaster. With communications tense, the daughter of a tech billionaire assembles her own team of specialists to try to destroy the asteroid before it is too late.
